name: Beautiful Neglect
description: Photo of a child's bedroom in an abandoned house. For the most part this place was nothing special, but this room captivated me - the partially painted window-frame, the peeling paint showing a beautiful purple beneath, the colorful fan in seemingly perfect condition without a speck of dust - to this day it's my number one favorite photo. Part of a series of 10 of my favorite drawings and photographs, now available as NFTs to hopefully help me recover from losing most of my crypto holdings.
